### Migration map — find and replace these exact values

Current → New:

  #000000 or #000            → var(--color-bg-primary)
  #111111 or #0a0a0a         → var(--color-bg-primary)
  #39FF14 (neon green)       → var(--color-accent)
  rgba(57,255,20,*)          → use --color-accent with matching opacity
  #ffffff body text          → var(--color-text-body)
  rgba(255,255,255,0.65)     → var(--color-text-body)
  rgba(255,255,255,0.45)     → var(--color-text-muted)
  rgba(255,255,255,0.3)      → var(--color-text-muted)
  white particle color       → #3A8FD4 (mid) and #B8DCFF (fg) in Three.js

  H1/H2 text: KEEP #ffffff — display headings stay pure white
  "Digital" outlined text stroke: change from white to 
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(77,175,255,0.4)
    (blue ghost instead of white ghost)

